metadata.name: Ether Faster
metadata.description:
In the web3 realm, "Ether Faster" was a legendary virtual circuit race that surpassed physical boundaries of blockchain technology. 

It symbolized more than just competition, conveying a powerful message: life is a race where triumph isn't solely about finishing first, but about facing challenges, surpassing limits, and uncovering our inner strength.

4500x4500 Pixel
2023
